                                                        Mathematics
Bit = 0 or 1
Nibble = "1 1 1 1"
Byte = "1111 1111"
Half Word = "1111 1111 1111 1111"
Word = "1111 1111 1111 1111 1111 1111 1111 1111"

Base 64 = If a answer keep the equal signs. Decode it usually.
==============================================================================================================================================
                                                                    OSI Layers
                                                        **EVERYTHING CAN BE FOUND IN SLIDES**
Application = Data Type - Data, 
              dis where i be doin stuff

Presentation = Data Type - Data . 
               Makes data presentable for the application to use it

Session = Data Type - Data . 
          PPTP - Old and unsecure vpn protocol
          L2TP - External encryption, better than PPTP
          SMB/CIFS -Server message block, cifs is open source.
          RPC - Interacts with server

Transport = TCP/UDP . Data Type - segments

Network = Data Type - packets . 
          Routers/ICMP/IP addresses

Data Link = Data type - frames . 
            LAN,WAN,MAN
            Sub-Layers = MAC is a sub-layer that controls access with the physical layer. (Media Access Control)
                         LLC is a sub layer that controls access with the network layer. (Logical Link Control)


Physical =  Data type is - bits
            Meduim of actual transportation.
