                                                                Headers
Standard MTU - 1500 Bytes

Ethernet Header - contains 8 bytes total, 7 bytes of 1's and 0's and a 1 byte delimeter. 
                  Ethertypes - (0800 = IPv4),(86DD = IPv6)

802.1Q Header - 

ARP Header - Offsets, 

IPv4 Header -   APIPA , RFC 3927
IPv6        -   SLAAC, RFC 4862


